data.description: GREAT FIND: WOW!! Crystal Lake views,Why is Crystal Lake Michigan so clear?  The watershed that feeds Crystal Lake is very small, and fertilizer and sewage outflows are minimal. Excellant clean/clear lake, Description: 724 acres in size with a maximum depth of 70 feet, all sports, fishing/swimming/boating/water-jet-ski and all, very good fishing lake, public access NE side of lake/large city park east side.  Enjoy the beauty of Mother Nature surounded by very well kept areas/eating places/roller-skating rink, surrounded by very nice rural communities.  Call for a private anytime -7-days a week for SHORT NOTICE SHOWS
